3400,/Hotel_Review-g186338-d193672-Reviews-or3400-Novotel_London_West-London_England.html#REVIEWS,Novotel London West Hotel Reviews,Good location for Apollo Theatre,"We chose the Novotel as a good location to attend a show at the Apollo Theatre and as we know the Hammersmith area well, we knew this was one of the best hotels with regards to location.  We arrived at the hotel just after midday expecting to leave our bags and collect them later when we returned to check in.  However, we were checked into our room immediately, which was a real bonus.  Although our hotel room was extremely clean, I do not know if the decor in the room was meant to be bland or attempting to be minimalist - but overall, the make-up of the room felt cheap.  Overall though, we had a great time revisiting Hammersmith and the hotel served the purpose that was intended.  I would stay at the hotel again, although, maybe it is time for it to be refurbishment.",Date of stay: October 2004,3.0
