3408,/Hotel_Review-g186338-d193672-Reviews-or3405-Novotel_London_West-London_England.html#REVIEWS,Novotel London West Hotel Reviews,Loved the Novotel London West in Hammersmith,"I recently stayed at the Novotel London West in Hammersmith. The building itself is new and modern, and my double room was very large, very comfortable, and very clean. The white walls reflected the natural and electric light giving the room a kind of cheeriness. It's about a five-minute walk from the hotel to the Hammersmith underground station, where you can take either the District Line, the Piccadilly Line, or the Hammersmith & City line to virtually anywhere in the central London area. If in the future I visit London again, I will definitely stay at the Novotel London West.",Date of stay: May 2004,4.0
